features: Outer Space Felt Board Set : OKOOKO oversize solar system felt board set comes with a 43x29 inch flannel felt board, 41 pieces felt figures and 2 sturdy hooks. Felt figures including Sun, eight planets, moon, Pluto, all planets name, astronaut, alien, rocket, meteorite, meteor and space satellite.

Educational Learning : This solar system felt board story set includes planets, space elements and the names of planets in Galaxy, kids can learn about space knowledge scientifically, and it can exercise kids imagination and hands-on ability. Great montessori teaching kit for preschool education, interactive time and storytelling.

Attractive Galaxy Design: Kids can place elements wherever they want to create various space stories. It would be a fun artistic expression play kit for whole family. Kids and parents can interact the various solar system elements to create a variety of creative educational scenes, it also great for kids’ imagination development.

Premium Material : OKOOKO 43x29 inch oversize felt board is made of superior flannel and felt, eco-friendly, non-toxic. Felt stories pieces are made of durable and sturdy felt with self-adhesive Velcro dots, no magnets needed, reusable.

Perfect Gift Choice: Ideal for preschool early education, storytelling, felt activity, quiet time, birthday gift, Christmas gift, and room decor. Kids will have fun with this felt story board set, it stimulates their imagination. It is also a beautiful decoration once assembled, perfect addition to classroom, bedroom, nursery and playroom.
